All of the internet servers were turned back on and we all quickly realized that the world had continued on without us. Because we were in isolation, the world had advanced much faster than we had and we soon found ourselves struggling to catch up. From internet video, we were able to learn of new technology that other countries produced. There were cars that flew and jetpacks too. It seemed that the traffic got so bad that people focused all their technological efforts on using the skies. 
here were also giant cities in the skyies that somehow just floated. 
The United States quickly learned that the world had continued to advance and it was no longer the center of technological and military supremacy.

The story begins with the US President informing the world that even though the US is still in ruins, it has decided to come out of isolation. All of the internet servers were turned back on and we all quickly realized that the world had continued on without us. Because we were in isolation, the world had advanced much faster than we had and we soon found ourselves struggling to catch up. From internet video, we were able to learn of new technology that other countries produced. There were cars that flew and jetpacks too. It seemed that the traffic got so bad that people focused all their technological efforts on using the skies. 
here were also giant cities in the skyies that somehow just floated. 
The United States quickly learned that the world had continued to advance and it was no longer the center of technological and military supremacy.
 There was peace all over the world too. It seems that they had all come out of isolation together for the purpose of developing the technology that would save them. The US was sadly left out though for fear that we would take over and steal all of the technology.

Because we were in isolation, the world had advanced much faster than we had and we soon found ourselves struggling to catch up.
